### Review Matrix

| Category | Strength | Improvement |
|----------|----------|-------------|
|  **Correctness** | Recurrence auto-creation works correctly for weekly, monthly, and yearly rules using `date-fns`. | `completeItem` marks the item completed before attempting the recurrence insert — no transaction means no rollback on failure. |
